Prediction: The predicted melting point for 4-amino-3-(morpholin-4-ylmethyl)-2H-chromen-2-one would be the sum of the increments over the melting point of benzene: 5.5 (benzene) + 80 (chromone) + 20 (amino group) + 10 (morpholine) + 5 (methylene bridge) = 120.5 degrees Celsius
